Package cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.solver.message

Messages and Listeners are used to allow communication from one source (usually solver) to several listeners.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Message Interface to allow implementations be used as messages for MessageListener as messages.
MessageListener Classes implementing MessageListener interface are able to accept messages.
 

Class Summary
MessageBetterConfigurationFound Notifies that better configuration was found (than current best one).
MessageOptimize Notifies of single optimize step.
MessageSolutionFound Notifies that new solution was found.
MessageSolverStart Notifies that optimization has started or been restarted in solver.
MessageSolverStop Notifies that optimization has started or been restarted in solver.
